{
  "texts": [
    "\"Processing\" the full text of a patent in a general and deep way can tell us even more about the underlying invention.",
    "Neural networks can be trained to identify particular invention attributes based on the text in the associated patents.",
    "The importance and impact of an invention are associated in complex ways with how the invention relates to those that came before and those that came after.",
    "As discussed below, NLP methods have been used extensively to make such comparisons and use them to quantify importance and impact.",
    "Second, NLP offers the prospect of identification of new proxies in the form of text artifacts that have not so far been thought of or collected for innovation research."
  ]
}